Read the other docs first :P

These are the current known issues, they should probably be merged into the TODO,
oh well they are here for now.  At least you get some docs :P

* No attachment content writing
* Reply/Forward is not implemented
* FCKeditor looses support for keyboard nav sometimes, why? nfi!
* php-pspell is required for spellchecking
	- aspell-cli may also be supported in the final version
* Only tested with desktop, probiz and verilak template sets
* Password are stored as plain text 
	- dodgy I know 
	- it is high on the list of things to fix
* No signature support
* No Admin/Prefs support
* POP3 support is broken atm :(
